data.description: Move right in! This cute 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home has an open floorplan - kitchen has a big granite island, double ovens in the stainless steel range and a new dishwasher. Living room has a gas starter fireplace, sunroom has tons of windows for lots of natural light. You will have a great view of the fenced backyard as well as the woods beyond the fence of this 1 acre +/- lot from the concrete patio and deck with built in swing. Large owner's suite with pretty walk-in shower and double vanity. Secondary bedrooms are both carpeted and share full bathroom with tub shower combo. Smooth ceilings and LVP. 2 car garage has shelving and a workbench with storage. Home has already been inspected! Agent is related to the sellers
